# Cloudflare Pages response headers for the standalone web build
# (dist/web — deployed by .github/workflows/deploy-web.yml). The CSP
# itself ships as a <meta> tag in src/web/index.html; this file adds the
# directives that CANNOT be expressed via meta (frame-ancestors-class
# protection via X-Frame-Options) plus standard hardening headers.
#
# Intentionally NOT set: Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy / -Opener-Policy —
# the app fetches runtime WASM from the R2 mirror and does not need
# SharedArrayBuffer, so COEP would only add cross-origin breakage risk.
#
# Harmless for the desktop build: file:// ignores this file entirely.

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()
